'''雷鬼樂'''（[[英文|英文]]：'''Reggae'''），又譯'''雷吉樂'''、'''瑞格樂'''、'''雷吉'''、'''雷鬼'''，是1960年代源自於[[牙買加|牙買加]]的一种[[音乐类型|音乐类型]]，也是是[[牙买加|牙买加]]或{{le|牙買加僑民|Jamaican diaspora}}的流行樂<ref>Stephen Davis. "Reggae." ''Grove Music Online''. ''Oxford Music Online''. Oxford University Press. Web.16 Feb 2016.</ref>。雷鬼的名稱源自牙買加某個街道名稱，意思是日常生活上一些瑣碎的事情。1968年由樂團{{le|Toots & The Maytals|Toots & The Maytals}}演唱的{{le|Do the Reggay|Do the Reggay}}是第一首出現Reggay的流行樂曲，為此音乐类型命名，也向大眾介紹雷鬼音樂<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.biography.com/people/frederick-toots-hibbert-10673303#acclaimed-musician |title=Frederick "Toots" Hibbert Biography |website=Biography.com |access-date=2 July 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809204903/http://www.biography.com/people/frederick-toots-hibbert-10673303#acclaimed-musician |archive-date=9 August 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dictionary.com/browse/reggae?s=t |title=reggae |website=Dictionary.com |access-date=10 July 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813063912/http://www.dictionary.com/browse/reggae?s=t |archive-date=13 August 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>。雷鬼音樂有時會用來指多种牙買加的舞曲總称<ref> {{cite book
 | author= Andy Bennett
 | coauthors= 孙忆南 
 | title= 流行音樂的文化 
 | year= 2004 
 | publisher= 書林出版有限公司 
 | location= 台北 
 | isbn= 9574450473 
 | pages= p.112
 | url=http://books.google.com.tw/books?id=SdD09GHS4bsC&pg=PA2055#v=onepage&q&f=false
}}</ref>，不過雷鬼音樂主要是指一種受到牙買加傳統{{le|門特|mento}}音樂、美國[[爵士乐|爵士乐]]和[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]影響的音樂，而且從早期的[[斯卡曲風|斯卡曲風]]和{{le|慢拍摇滚|rocksteady}}所衍生的新音樂類型<ref name="Return of Reggae">{{cite news|author=Geoffey Himes |title=Return of Reggae |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=28 January 1979 }}</ref>。雷鬼音樂常和新聞、社會八卦以及政治評論有關<ref>"Reggae." ''The Oxford Dictionary of Music'', 2nd ed. rev. Ed. Michael Kennedy. ''Oxford Music Online''.Oxford University Press. Web. 16 February 2016.</ref>。雷鬼音樂的特點是其貝斯吉他和鼓強拍的對位，以及其反拍節奏部分。雷鬼音樂是起源於斯卡曲風和慢拍摇滚，雷鬼音樂類似慢拍摇滚一樣，用貝斯作為節奏樂器<ref>Wilton, Peter. "reggae." ''The Oxford Companion to Music''. Ed. Alison Latham. ''Oxford Music Online''.Oxford University Press. Web. 16 February 2016.</ref>。

雷鬼音樂和[[拉斯塔法里运动|拉斯塔法里运动]]有密切的關係，拉斯塔法里运动是{{le|非洲中心主义|Afrocentrism|非洲中心}}的宗教，自1930年代從牙買加發展，主要是提倡[[泛非主义|泛非主义]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Warner|first=Keith Q.|date=1988|title=Calypso, reggae, and Rastafarianism: Authentic Caribbean voices|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_popular-music-and-society_spring-1988_12_1/page/53|journal=Popular Music and Society|language=en|volume=12|issue=1|pages=53–62|doi=10.1080/03007768808591306|issn=0300-7766}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite thesis|last=Earl|first=Bunn, Glenn|title=The Influence of Rastafarianism and Reggae Music on Jamaican and International Politics|date=2005|publisher=St. John Fisher College|url=https://fisherpub.sjfc.edu/intlstudies_masters/42/|language=en|access-date=30 November 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201005104/https://fisherpub.sjfc.edu/intlstudies_masters/42/|archive-date=1 December 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Campbell|first=Horace|date=1988|title=Rastafari as Pan Africanism in the Caribbean and Africa|journal=African Journal of Political Economy|volume=2|issue=1|pages=75–88|jstor=23500303}}</ref>。在拉斯塔法里运动普及之後，隨著拉斯塔法里运动以及其教義開始被人所知，雷鬼音樂也開始在全世界流行<ref name=":0" />。雷鬼音樂是傳播拉斯塔法里运动主要信息的重要工具，音樂家成為了信息傳遞者，如拉斯塔法里运动所提到的：「士兵和-{}-音樂家是帶來改變的工具。」<ref>{{Cite book|title=Reggae bloodlines : in search of the music and culture of Jamaica|last=Davis|first=Stephen|date=1992|publisher=Da Capo Press|isbn=978-0306804960|edition=1st Da Capo Press|location=New York|oclc=26014673|url=https://archive.org/details/reggaebloodlines00davi}}</ref>。

在音樂風格上，雷鬼音樂結合了[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]、[[爵士乐|爵士乐]]以及{{le|門特|mento}}（慶祝用的鄉間音樂，是農村大眾的舞曲，也取代了讚美詩和當地教堂歌唱的改編聖歌）<ref name="Grove Music Online">{{cite book|author=Stephen Davis |title=Reggae |publisher=The New Grove Dictionary of Jazz |edition= second }}</ref>、卡里普索音樂（calypso）,<ref>Anderson, Rick. "Reggae Music: A History and Selective Discography”. ''Notes'' 61.1 (2004): 206–214.</ref>，也受到傳統非洲民間節奏的影響。雷鬼音樂中最容易識別的是其反拍節奏，由吉他或網鋼琴在反拍上所彈奏的斷奏和弦。其強拍在二、四拍上。雷鬼音樂的速度一般會比斯卡曲風和慢拍摇滚要慢<ref name="All About Jazz">{{cite web |author=All About Jazz |url=http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/article.php?id=34239 |title=Various Artists | Rocksteady: The Roots Of Reggae |website=Allaboutjazz.com |date=2009-10-01 |access-date=2012-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120202181642/http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/article.php?id=34239 |archive-date=2012-02-02 |url-status=live }}</ref>。在雷鬼音樂中可以看到[[对唱|对唱]]的概念。雷鬼乐的代表人物是[[巴布·馬利|巴布·馬利]]（Bob Marley，又译作鲍勃·马莱，1945年-1981年），他带动了雷鬼乐的流行<ref>{{cite news| author=江家華| title=辭世30年 雷鬼教父巴布馬利 影響力不墜| url=http://news.chinatimes.com/reading/110513/112012102900328.html| work=中時電子報| publisher=中時集團| date=2012-10-29| accessdate=2013-07-17| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102225238/http://news.chinatimes.com/reading/110513/112012102900328.html| archivedate=2012-11-02}}</ref>。雷鬼音樂流派是由鼓和貝斯所主導<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.britannica.com/art/reggae|title=Reggae – music|website=Britannica.com|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318144350/https://www.britannica.com/art/reggae|archive-date=18 March 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20100416170447/http://debate.uvm.edu/dreadlibrary/Havel.htm]</ref>。主要的樂手有{{le|Toots and the Maytals|Toots and the Maytals}}樂團的{{le|傑克·傑克遜 (貝斯手)|Jackie Jackson (bassist)|傑克·傑克遜}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/entertainment/Jackie-Jackson--Bass-player-extraordinaire|title=Jackie Jackson: Bass player extraordinaire|newspaper=Jamaica Observer|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206002617/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/entertainment/Jackie-Jackson--Bass-player-extraordinaire|archive-date=6 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>、[[鲍勃·马利与哭泣者乐队|鲍勃·马利与哭泣者乐队]]的{{le|Carlton Barrett|Carlton Barrett}}<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-drummers-of-all-time-20160331/carlton-barrett-20160328|title=100 Greatest Drummers of All Time|magazine=Rolling Stone|access-date=9 May 2018|date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206073510/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-drummers-of-all-time-20160331/carlton-barrett-20160328|archive-date=6 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>、{{le|The Skatalites|The Skatalites}}中的{{le|Lloyd Brevett|Lloyd Brevett}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/46331/skatalites-bassist-lloyd-brevett-dead-at-80|title=Skatalites Bassist Lloyd Brevett Dead at 80|website=Billboard.com|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512014128/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/46331/skatalites-bassist-lloyd-brevett-dead-at-80|archive-date=12 May 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>、Toots and the Maytals的{{le|保羅・道格拉斯|Paul Douglas (musician)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://daily.redbullmusicacademy.com/2013/06/toots-and-the-maytals-live-album|title=Red Bull Music Academy Daily|website=Daily.redbullmusicacademy.com|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629074330/http://daily.redbullmusicacademy.com/2013/06/toots-and-the-maytals-live-album|archive-date=29 June 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>、The Skatalites的{{le|Lloyd Knibb|Lloyd Knibb}}<ref>"Lloyd Knibb revolutionised Jamaican drumming, says PJ". Jamaica Observer. Web. 27 May 2011. <{{cite web |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/entertainment/Lloyd-Knibb-revolutionised-Jamaican-drumming--says-PJ_8867991 |title=Archived copy |access-date=28 May 2011 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110530040025/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/entertainment/Lloyd-Knibb-revolutionised-Jamaican-drumming--says-PJ_8867991 |archive-date=30 May 2011 }}> Retrieved 22 November 2016.</ref>、{{le|Winston Grennan|Winston Grennan}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/04/nyregion/winston-grennan-56-jamaican-drummer.html|title=Winston Grennan, 56, Jamaican Drummer|first=Jon|last=Pareles|date=4 November 2000|access-date=9 May 2018|website=Nytimes.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203184745/http://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/04/nyregion/winston-grennan-56-jamaican-drummer.html|archive-date=3 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>、{{le|Sly Dunbar|Sly Dunbar}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/people/literature-and-arts/music-popular-and-jazz-biographies/sly-and-robbie|title=Sly and Robbie facts, information, pictures – Encyclopedia.com articles about Sly and Robbie|website=Encyclopedia.com|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510193816/https://www.encyclopedia.com/people/literature-and-arts/music-popular-and-jazz-biographies/sly-and-robbie|archive-date=10 May 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>和來自{{le|The Upsetters|The Upsetters}}的Anthony "Benbow" Creary<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dDKfGRCq73cC&q=benbow&pg=PA308|title=Caribbean Popular Music: An Encyclopedia of Reggae, Mento, Ska, Rock Steady, and Dancehall|first=David Vlado|last=Moskowitz|date=9 May 2018|page=308|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|access-date=9 May 2018|via=Google Books|isbn=9780313331589}}</ref>。[[電貝斯|貝斯吉他]]在雷鬼音樂中的角色很重要。雷鬼音樂中的貝斯樂音很粗重，而且經過{{le|等化器 (聲音)|equalization (audio)|等化器}}處理，以去掉其高頻音，強調其低頻音。雷鬼音樂中的[[吉他|吉他]]多半是在反拍時彈奏。雷鬼音樂常會用[[牙买加方言|牙买加方言]]、{{le|牙買加英文|Jamaican English}}或{{le|伊亞里克|Iyaric}}方言演唱。雷鬼音樂的歌詞會強調社會批判以及其宗教上的傳統<ref name="It's About New Beginnings And Keeping the Faith">{{cite news|author=Ben Ratliff |title=It's About New Beginnings And Keeping the Faith |newspaper=The New York Times |date=20 September 1999 |page= 5}}</ref>，不過許多的雷鬼音樂也會討論比較不沈重，比較個人的主題，例如愛和社交。

雷鬼音樂已擴展到世界上的許多國家，常配合當地的樂器演奏，也會和其他的音樂融合。{{le|西班牙雷鬼|Reggae en Español}}從中美洲西班牙語的巴拿馬開始，擴展到南美大陸的[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]、[[圭亚那|圭亚那]]，之後擴展到其他國家。{{le|英國的加勒比音樂|Caribbean music in the United Kingdom}}（其中也包括雷鬼音樂），自1960年代就開始流行，也演變出許多的子流派，也和其他的音樂融合。許多雷鬼樂手的音樂生涯是從英國開始的，也有許多歐洲藝人以及樂團從歐洲的牙買加和加勒比群體中取得靈感。1970年代后，雷鬼樂開始成為主流[[流行音樂|流行音樂]]曲風之一，眾多樂隊歌聲紛紛效仿，其中以[[英國|英國]]的[[UB40|UB40]]和[[警察乐队|警察乐队]]最为知名。非洲的雷鬼音樂是從[[巴布·馬利|巴布·馬利]]在1980年代訪問辛巴威開始流行。在牙買加，雷鬼音樂的授權是一大收入來源<ref>Bennetzen, Jørgen, and Kirsten Maegaard. "Reggae". ''Fontes Artis Musicae'' 29.4 (1982): 182–186.</ref>。2018年，雷鬼音樂被列入[[聯合國教科文組織|聯合國教科文組織]]的[[非物質文化遺產|非物質文化遺產]]。<ref name="unesco">{{cite web |title=Reggae music of Jamaica |url=https://ich.unesco.org/en/RL/reggae-music-of-jamaica-01398 |publisher=UNESCO Culture Sector |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129090119/https://ich.unesco.org/en/RL/reggae-music-of-jamaica-01398 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/nov/29/un-adds-reggae-music-to-list-of-international-cultural-treasures|title=UN adds reggae music to list of international cultural treasures|last=Snapes|first=Laura|date=2018-11-29|website=The Guardian|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-11-30}}</ref>

== 关于称呼 ==
* 廣義上指牙買加境內流行音樂，但也包含[[斯卡曲風|斯卡曲風]]、{{link-en|慢拍摇滚|Rocksteady}}或者{{link-en|dub|dub}}。

== 音樂特性 ==
[[File:Reggae_double_riff_on_D_and_Em64.png|thumb]]
雷鬼樂採用了一些[[節奏藍調|節奏藍調]]（R&B）、[[爵士乐|爵士乐]]、{{link-en|门特|Mento}}音樂、{{link-en|卡里普索音樂|Calypso music}}、非洲音樂及拉美音樂中的一些元素。

雷鬼樂的[[拍號|拍號]]一般會是4/4拍，由於其平衡的節奏不太適合其他的[[拍號|拍號]]．例如3/4拍。雷鬼樂中最容易識別的是其弱拍的節奏。由吉他或鋼琴（或二者都有）演奏的斷音．一般稱為{{link-en|Skank|Ska stroke}}。

雷鬼樂的重音在每個[[小節|小節]]的第二拍及第四拍，而且用鼓強調第三拍，創造出一個獨特的感受。雷鬼的弱拍可以視為在重音在「1 and 2 and 3 and 4 and etc」的and上，和其他流行音樂的强拍恰好相反<ref>Levitin, Daniel J. (2006). ''[[This_Is_Your_Brain_On_Music|This Is Your Brain On Music]]'', pp. 113-114 ISBN 978-0-452-28852-2.</ref>。

雷鬼樂的節奏一般比[[斯卡曲風|斯卡]]或慢拍搖滾要慢<ref>{{cite web |author=All About Jazz |url=http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/article.php?id=34239 |title=Various Artists | Rocksteady: The Roots Of Reggae |publisher=Allaboutjazz.com |date=2009-10-01 |accessdate=2012-05-29 |archive-date=2012-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120202181642/http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/article.php?id=34239 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其特點是較慢的節奏、吉他或鋼琴的弱拍、強調第三拍，以及由[[切分音|切分音]]組成，旋律性的低音线，這些特質使雷鬼樂不同於其他音樂。

